document_data.Combat:
A juju zombie could use tools, use throwing weapons, as well as bows and crossbows. Jujus partially existed on the [[Negative Material Plane]] making them only vulnerable to magical weapons. These zombies were also immune to mind-affecting spells, illusion, poison, electricity, ''[[magic missile|magic missiles]]'', death, and cold spells. They also had resistance to fire.
Jujus could understand language and take commands, they preferred simple tactics and strategies in combat. They were dexterous enough to easily scale and climb walls with ease.{{Cite book/Monstrous Compendium Volume One
|144}}
